==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tayra
<hw>Tay"ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From the native
name.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A South American carnivore
(<spn>Galera barbara</spn>) allied to the grison. The tail is long and
thick. The length, including the tail, is about three feet.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>taira</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tay-Sachs Disease</ent>⟦br⟧
